
### Just Build:

Optional cleanup:

```
\rm -rf ~/.gradle/
```

Enter dev env:

```
nix-shell
steam-run bash
```

Specify SDK location either in `ANDROID_HOME` env var or add `sdk.dir=/path/to/sdk` in `local.properties`.

```
export ANDROID_HOME=/plan/2-dev/android/sdk
./gradlew assembleDebug
```

### Cli adb phone live debugging

```
nix-shell
adb start-server
steam-run bash
./gradlew installDebug
[ At some point you will have to give permission from your phone. ]
adb uninstall com.woynert.boringbrowser
adb shell am start -n com.woynert.boringbrowser/.MainActivity
adb shell run-as com.woynert.boringbrowser logcat --format=color
```

Run + Launch + Filter logs.

./gradlew installDebug && ./gradlew installDebug && adb shell am start -n com.woynert.boringbrowser/.MainActivity && adb logcat -s BoringBrowserDebug


